---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms of Service - Dev Cockpit"
  description="Dev Cockpit terms of service. Understand your rights and responsibilities when using our app."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">Effective Date: September 1, 2025</p>
      
      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            By downloading, installing, or using Dev Cockpit ("the App"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree to these Terms, do not use the App.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. Description of Service</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            Dev Cockpit is a premium macOS application that provides developer tools including:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li>Homebrew package management interface</li>
            <li>Port monitoring and security analysis</li>
            <li>Network diagnostic tools</li>
            <li>AI-powered insights using Apple Intelligence</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mt-4">
            All features operate locally on your Mac without cloud dependencies.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Subscription Terms</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">3.1 Free Trial</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            New users receive a 7-day free trial with full access to all features. No credit card is required to start the trial. The trial begins when you first launch the App.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">3.2 Subscription Plans</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            After the trial period, continued use requires a subscription:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li>Monthly: €14.99 per month</li>
            <li>Annual: €149 per year (save 17%)</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">3.3 Payment Processing</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            All payments are processed through Paddle, our payment processor. Paddle's terms and conditions apply to all transactions. We do not have direct access to your payment information.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">3.4 Renewal and Cancellation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            Subscriptions automatically renew unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can manage or cancel your subscription through your account portal or by contacting support.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. License Grant</h2>
