          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mt-4">
            Our total liability shall not exceed the amount you paid for the App in the twelve months preceding the claim.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">9. Indemnification</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Dev Cockpit from any claims, damages, losses, liabilities, costs, and expenses arising from your use of the App or violation of these Terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">10. Refund Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee. If you're not satisfied with Dev Cockpit within 30 days of purchase, contact support@devcockpit.app for a full refund. Refunds are processed through Paddle.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">11. Updates and Modifications</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            We may update the App and these Terms from time to time. Continued use of the App after changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms. We recommend reviewing these Terms periodically.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
