          <p class="text-gray-300">
            These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the European Union and Portugal, without regard to conflict of law principles.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">14. Severability</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            If any provision of these Terms is found to be unenforceable or invalid, that provision shall be limited or eliminated to the minimum extent necessary, and the remaining provisions shall remain in full effect.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">15. Contact Information</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            For questions about these Terms, please contact us:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:legal@devcockpit.app" class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300">legal@devcockpit.app</a></li>
            <li>Website: <a href="/support" class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300">devcockpit.app/support</a></li>
          </ul>
